                        &lt;/span&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;+1  Sometimes, it&apos;s good to just get a short one-liner like mentioned in this answer: &quot;In short, use this &apos;if &lt;b&gt;name&lt;/b&gt; == &quot;main&quot; &apos; block to prevent (certain) code from being run when the module is imported.&quot;. This is useful. Thanks!&lt;/span&gt;

