            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;Hi, you are one of  the few that addressed the question referring to the multithreaded aspect. May I ask you this, what happens if I have code outside of &quot;main&quot; and not encapsulated inside a function? Will this code get executed again and again by every new thread started from main?&lt;/span&gt;

              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/11990618/welsige&quot; title=&quot;129 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;Welsige&lt;/a&gt;
