            &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;I kept the example code simple to avoid distractions; in real life, you need to cope with &lt;code&gt;input&lt;/code&gt; returning something which isn&apos;t a number, and of course, a real-life Fibonacci function should perhaps be optimized to avoid recalculating the beginning of the sequence every time you call it.&lt;/span&gt;

              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
