            &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;The &lt;code&gt;n: int&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code&gt;-&amp;gt; int&lt;/code&gt; type annotations require Python &amp;gt;= 3.6&lt;/span&gt;

              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/874188/tripleee&quot; title=&quot;159,777 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;tripleee&lt;/a&gt;
